>If you set header, or footer in global layout, then all pages have its header and footer.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"alert alert-info alert-light\">Each layout affects pages belong to its display condition.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>If you set blog layout as above screenshot, your blog page looks like this.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img width=\"1024\" height=\"738\" src=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder-2-1024x738.jpg\" alt=\"layout-builder-blog\" class=\"wp-image-1538\" srcset=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder-2-1024x738.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder-2-300x216.jpg 300w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder-2-768x554.jpg 768w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder-2-150x108.jpg 150w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder-2.jpg 1300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><figcaption>Blog Page<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"mt-7 mb-3\">Layout Categories<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>Layout categories are groups of layouts divided by display condition. Learn <a href=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/2021\/10\/25\/how-to-create-a-layout\/\" data-type=\"URL\">how to create<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"mb-6\"><li><strong>All Layouts<\/strong> &#8211; Show all layouts.<\/li><li><strong>Home<\/strong> &#8211; Show layouts applied for only home page.<\/li><li><strong>Portfolios<\/strong>&#8211; Show layouts applied for only portfolio archive pages such as portfolios page, portfolio category pages, portfolio skill pages.<\/li><li><strong>Portfolio Item<\/strong>&#8211; Show page layouts applied for single portfolio pages.<\/li><li><strong>Blog<\/strong> &#8211; Show layouts applied for only post archive pages such as blog page, post category pages, tag pages.<\/li><li><strong>Single Post<\/strong>&#8211; Show page layouts applied for single post pages.<\/li><li><strong>Members<\/strong>&#8211; Show layouts applied for only member archive pages such as members page and member category pages.<\/li><li><strong>Member Item<\/strong>&#8211; Show page layouts applied for single member pages.<\/li><li><strong>Search<\/strong> &#8211; Show search layouts applied for only search pages.<\/li><li><strong>Page<\/strong> &#8211; Show page layouts applied for only real pages.<\/li><li><strong>404 Page<\/strong> &#8211; Show 404 page layout (well known as &#8220;page not found&#8221;)<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<h5 class=\"mt-7 mb-3\">Page Layout<\/h5>\n\n\n\n<p>Page layout is a set of <a href=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/2021\/10\/26\/layout-builder-options\/\" data-type=\"URL\">options<\/a> about used blocks, sidebars. And it affects pages belong to its <a href=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/2021\/10\/26\/how-to-set-condition-to-a-layout\/\" data-type=\"URL\">display condition<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large is-resized mt-3\"><img src=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder3-1024x751.jpg\" alt=\"layout-builder3\" class=\"wp-image-3604\" width=\"1011\" height=\"741\" srcset=\"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder3-1024x751.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder3-300x220.jpg 300w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder3-768x563.jpg 768w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder3-150x110.jpg 150w, https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-content\/uploads\/sites\/17\/2021\/10\/layout-builder3.jpg 1253w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1011px) 100vw, 1011px\" \/><figcaption>Page Layout<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>UDesign Layout Builder is a tool that apply any layouts to any pages on your website. To open layout builder, please click UDesign &gt; Layout Builder menu in admin&#8217;s main menu. Then, you can see some layouts already added by the theme. Global layout affects all pages. If you set header, or footer in global [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1520"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=1520"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1520\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4037,"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/1520\/revisions\/4037"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/d-themes.com\/wordpress\/udesign\/documentation\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1520"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddabl